data.description:
BACK ON MARKET | NO FAULT TO SELLER | Welcome home to this stunning home situated in the heart of Yukon. Located just south of Main Street, you will enjoy access to the pond across the street, walking trails, and a quick jot to the Mabel C. Fry Public Library. Skyview Elementary, Sunrise Park and the splash pad is just walking distance away with many other amenities nearby. 

This two owner home features impact resistant shingles, new carpet in 2022, new paint, and a wonderful functional floor plan. 

Downstairs you will find the primary suite, indoor laundry room, the adorable half bathroom, kitchen, dining and main living area. The living room features beautiful built-in cabinetry and a gas fireplace with a vaulted ceiling. The expansive window over the kitchen sinks adds so much natural light. 

Head upstairs to find the additional 3 bedrooms and a full bathroom. The backyard is large with a covered patio for your outdoor living retreat. Enjoy quiet evenings for years to come! 

You'll love the quick access to the Turnpike and I-40. This is your chance to jump on a low interest rate and own to your perfect Yukon home! Don't wait this gorgeous home will sell quickly!
